parameters:
\SE[74]Phew... I received a signal from Cat... \SE[75]For now, it
seems like I managed to do it successfully.

\SE[58]I wonder if it's still too early for me to stand on my
own... \!\SE[75]But I'm already more capable than the graduates
of the academy....

\SE[60]Thinking too much about being overprotective is also
something to consider.... \!\SE[61]If I meddle too much, I might
end up taking away the opportunity for those kids to achieve
their own accomplishments....

\SE[84]Sigh... I'm worried. I hope they're not injured....
\SE[59]I guess being a mentor isn't really my thing, huh....
Ahh!! It's cold!! I'm gonna die!! I'm gonna die...!!!
